.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, juice, soy-milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, crime, drama, mystery
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, poppy, orchid, lily
1. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who growsorchid##1
2. the person who growslily is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
6. the person who growslily is the person drinking juice##1
7. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growslily##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | juice     | almond-milk | iced-tea |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | animation | drama       | crime    |
| Flower   | poppy   | lily | azalea    | orchid |

