.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, cooking, dancing, traveling
There 4 different types of food: orange, zucchini, watermelon, eggplant
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, german, pakistani, spanish
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person eating orange##1
2. the person eating eggplant is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the spanish is on the left of the canadian##1
4. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is the pakistani##1
7. the spanish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | traveling   | dancing   | card-games | cooking |
| Food   | watermelon | orange | zucchini   | eggplant |
| Nationality   | spanish     | canadian  | pakistani  | german  |

